<DOCHDR>
http://www.sbsc.org:80/townhall/character.html 204.71.237.86 19970108015903 text/html 20199
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 01:59:16 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 24-Oct-96 09:47:11 GMT
Content-length: 20010
Content-type: text/html
