http://www.sbsc.org:80/sbsc/tax-1196.html 204.71.237.86 19970108020004 text/html 3516
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 02:00:20 GMT
Last-modified: Thursday, 19-Dec-96 16:53:10 GMT
