<center><h2>Features</h2></center>
<p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/abic/kickoff.html.cgi">Welcome</a> 
 to ABIC's web site! ABIC Director <a href="/abic/cdmbio.html.cgi">Cleta Mitchell</a> describes 
the site and what we hope you'll gain from it.
<P>

<li>
Term Limits to be the <a href="/abic/newtspeech.html.cgi">First Item of Business</a> in
the House in the 105th Congress!
<p>

<li><a href="/abic/tlqa.html.cgi">Term Limits Questions and Answers:</a> ABIC has developed this page to help set some of the anti-term limit myths aside
     once and for all.<p>

<li>What were the Presidential candidates' positions on term limits?  Find out in <a href=
"/ab
ic/preztlpos.html.cgi">ABIC's Quick-Read Summary</a>
