7%		STRONGLY FAVORABLE
26%		SOMEWHAT FAVORABLE
33%	TOTAL FAVORABLE
23%		SOME UNFAVORABLE
29%		STRONGLY UNFAVORABLE
52%	TOTAL UNFAVORABLE
13% 		NO OPINION
1%		NEVER HEARD OF
2%		DON'T KNOW/ REFUSED
</pre><P><b>
7.	 John Sweeney/AFL-CIO President John Sweeney</b><p><pre>
