14%		SOMEWHAT FAVORABLE
20%	TOTAL FAVORABLE
5%		SOMEWHAT UNFAVORABLE
4%		STRONGLY UNFAVORABLE
9%	TOTAL UNFAVORABLE
22% 		NO OPINION
47%		NEVER HEARD OF
2%		DON'T KNOW/REFUSED
