<DOCHDR>
http://www.sbsc.org:80/bradley/curint.html 204.71.237.86 19970108022831 text/html 5891
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 02:28:47 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 30-Aug-96 18:19:35 GMT
