<DOCNO>WT16-B02-196</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA022-000238-B004-379</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.sbsc.org:80/bradley/gpurp.html 204.71.237.86 19970108022856 text/html 3827
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
