<blockquote>
<img src="/crc/images/nanny.gif" alt="Book Cover" align="right">
<P>
<h2> The Rise of the Nanny State: How Consumer Advocates Try to Run Our Lives</h2>
(<a href="/crc/about/pubs.html">Ordering Information</a>)<br><P>
<a href="#summ">Executive Summary</a>
<P>
<h3>Table of Contents</h3>
<ul>
Preface
<P>
<b>Introduction</b> An Age of Maturity
<P>
<b>Chapter One</b> From <I>The Jungle</I> to the Great Society
<P>
<b>Chapter Two</b> Naderites and Lawyers
<P>
<b>Chapter Three</b> Food and Science:  Creating a Pseudo-Crisis
<P>
<b>Chapter Four</b> Consumer Nannyism:  Label Madness and the New Puritanism
<P>
<b>Chapter Five</b> The Anti-Destination League
<P>
<b>Chapter Six</b> Consumerists and Government Medicine
<P>
<b>Chapter Seven</b>How to Restrain Big Nanny Government
<P>
