<dt>

   <IMG ALIGN=left SRC  = "images/button.gif" HSPACE=5 vspace=5>

   <img src="images/new.gif" align="right">

<a href="edit/hersch.htm"><b>Land For War: Israel, Netanyahu, and Peace</b></a> 
<dd>

    -- By Bruce Herschensohn
<P>
<I> Benjamin Netanyahu's victory in Israel could head off "Land for War," but the U.S. government should give him the support he needs and deserves.</I>
<p>
<br clear=all>

<dt>

   <IMG ALIGN=left SRC  = "images/button.gif" HSPACE=5 vspace=5>

   <img src="images/new.gif" align="right">

<a href="edit/plessy.htm"><b>Anniversaries For Dissenters:</b></a> The 100th Anniversary of <I>Plessy v. Ferguson.</I>

<dd>

    -- By Ken Masugi
<P>
<I> Saturday, May 18, 1996 marked 100 years since the U.S. Supreme Court's Plessy v. Ferguson decision. A reflection on the bitter legacy of 'seperate but equal.'</I>
