<center>

   <img src="images/title.gif">

</center>

<P>

<hr noshade>

<P>

This section is an index for the Golden State Papers Series.  This is a collection of 
policy papers published by the <B>Claremont Institute</B>, beginning in 1989, and covering a range of topics affecting law and policy in California, such as education, welfare, civll rights, privitization of public utilities, and much more.
