<html><head>
<title>The Claremont Institute Publications</title>
</head>

<body bgcolor=#ffffff>

<center>

<table border=0 width=580><tr><td>

<center>

   <img src="images/pubtitl.gif" ALT="Claremont Institute Publications">

</center>

<P>

<hr noshade>

<P>

The following are a select group of papers and monographs published by the Claremont Institute from 1995 to 1996. 

<P>

<hr noshade>

<P>

<ul>

<li>
	<a href="affirm/index.html">New Civil Rights Publications: "A Citizen's Guide to the Affirmative Action Debate," "The Affirmative Action Trainwreck," and more!</a>

	<img src="images/new.gif">

<P>
<li>
