<html><head><title>Empower America Mission Statement</title></head>
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
<center>
<img src="/empower/empower.gif" alt="Empower America Logo"><P>
<hr size="3" width="50%">
<br><h2>What Is Empower America?</h2>
<hr width="30%" size="3">
</center>
<br><P>
<center>
<h3>
<a href="/empower/eamissn.html">Empower America Mission Statement</a>
<p>
<a href="/empower/appltr.html">Empower America Internship Program</a>
<p>
<a href="/empower/intouch.html">How to get in touch with Empower America</a>
<p>
<a href="/empower/moreinfo.html">Request More Information</a>
</h3>
</center>
<br><p>
