<DOCHDR>
http://www.sbsc.org:80/mrc/mediawatch/96conve.html 204.71.237.86 19970108024320 text/html 45266
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 02:43:34 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 20-Sep-96 18:04:57 GMT
Content-length: 45079
