<DOCHDR>
http://www.sbsc.org:80/savers/legislation/iiasumm.html 204.71.237.86 19970108024723 text/html 2175
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Wednesday, 08-Jan-97 02:47:40 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 10-Sep-96 19:54:32 GMT
