<HTML>    
<HEAD>    
<TITLE>League Objectives</TITLE>    
</HEAD>    
<BODY>    
<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" LINK="#2F4F2F" VLINK="#3232CD">
<img src="/savers/images/tnygrngr.gif" alt=" "><FONT size=5><b><a name="obj">League 
Objectives</a></b></FONT><BR>    
<img src="/savers/images/smgrnln1.gif">
<br>
<P>   
<center><b><i>Your wealth is &quot;wealth&quot; no matter how small or large.<br>   
You must protect it from improper, confiscatory, taxes.</i></b></center><br>   
<p>   
The League's primary objective is to remove the government's senseless    
tax bias against private savings and investments. By building a broad base of voter/taxpayer activists,   
spanning all age groups and income    
levels, the League:<BR>    
<p>   
<ul>   
<li> Works toward the development and adoption of clear, concise, tax laws that   
 promote increased private saving and investing.<BR>   
<br>   
<li> Works with members of Congress and the Administration to support    
or defeat legislation which affects the taxation of private savings and    
investments.<BR>   
<br>   
<li> Communicates with voter/taxpayers, as well as with financial    
institutions, employers, unions, and the media.<br>    
<br>   
<li> Builds coalitions with like-minded groups, unions, and associations.<br>   
<BR>   
<li> Tracks and reports upon relevant legislation as it makes its    
way through the congressional maze.<BR>    
<br>   
<li> Informs the media on current savings and investment taxation issues in    
order to generate broad, public appreciation and understanding    
of this vital subject.<BR>   
</ul>   
<p>    
<hr>   
[<a href="/savers/">Home</a>]   
 </BODY>    
    
</HTML>    
   



