<center>
<h2>Press Releases</h2>
</center>
<hr>
<p>
<blockquote>
<ul>
<LI>October 18, 1995:  <a href="/taxcom/cspan.html">"Tax Reform Commissioners to Appear on C-Span"</a>
<LI>September 26, 1995:  <a href="/taxcom/clevelan.html">"National Tax Reform Commission to Hold Cleveland Hearing"</a>
