<A NAME="linkTOP"><BODY BGCOLOR="#ffffff" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#ff0800"
VLINK="#6f6f6f" ALINK="#000000"></A>
<center><IMG SRC="../images/twtbanner.gif" WIDTH=375 HEIGHT=42 ALIGN=MIDDLE ALT="The Washington Times" border=0><BR>
<IMG SRC="../images/nwe.redrule.gif" WIDTH=520 HEIGHT=24 ALIGN=MIDDLE border=0><BR></NOBR><font size=-1>Published in Washington, D.C.<IMG SRC="../images/nop.gif" ALT="" ALIGN=top WIDTH=80 HEIGHT=0>&#009;<B>December 29, 1996 -- Edition</B>&#009;<IMG SRC="../images/nop.gif" ALT="" ALIGN=top WIDTH=80 HEIGHT=0>"America's Newspaper"<BR></font></NOBR><A HREF="buttons.3.gif.map"><MAP NAME="clientmap9"><AREA SHAPE=RECT COORDS="436,1,519,18" HREF="#linkTOP"><AREA SHAPE=RECT COORDS="351,1,428,16" HREF="../letters/letters.html"><AREA SHAPE=RECT COORDS="263,0,345,19" HREF="../stories/exclusive.html"><AREA SHAPE=RECT COORDS="177,1,257,18" HREF="../stories/culture.html"><AREA SHAPE=RECT COORDS="90,0,172,19" HREF="../stories/top.html"><AREA SHAPE=RECT COORDS="2,1,86,18" HREF="../index.html"></MAP><IMG SRC="images/buttons.3.gif" WIDTH=520 HEIGHT=19 ALIGN=MIDDLE ALT="Navigation Bar graphic, see text links below." border=0 USEMAP="#clientmap9" ISMAP></A><BR><IMG SRC="../images/nop.gif"  ALIGN=top WIDTH=0 HEIGHT=8><BR><TABLE BORDER=0 CELLSPACING=0 CELLPADDING=0 WIDTH=520><TR ALIGN=Left VALIGN=Top> <TD ALIGN=Left VALIGN=Top COLSPAN="3" ROWSPAN="5"><TABLE BORDER=0 CELLSPACING=0 CELLPADDING=0 WIDTH=325><TR ALIGN=Left VALIGN=Top> <TD ALIGN=Left VALIGN=Top COLSPAN="1" ROWSPAN="1"><center><font size=7><I>Watch This Space<BR></I></font><FONT SIZE=4>News about <I>The Washington Times</I></FONT></center><FONT SIZE=6><center><B>Grand jury indicts principal for attack on reporter</center></B></FONT><BR><IMG SRC="../images/nop.gif" ALT="" ALIGN=top WIDTH=30 HEIGHT=0>A grand jury on Dec. 19 indicted Marcus Garvey Charter School Principal Mary A.T. Anigbo and three school employees in the Dec. 3 assaults on a reporter and photographer for The Washington Times and two D.C. police officers.<BR><IMG SRC="../images/nop.gif" ALT="" ALIGN=top WIDTH=30 HEIGHT=0>The four school employees were indicted on misdemeanor charges that included simple assault and taking property without right for the attack, in which the principal took a note pad from Susan Ferrechio, a reporter for The Times.<BR><IMG SRC="../images/nop.gif" ALT="" ALIGN=top WIDTH=30 HEIGHT=0>The grand jury did not return hate-crime indictments from the incident, in which each side accused the other of making racially charged threats.<BR><IMG SRC="../images/nop.gif" ALT="" ALIGN=top WIDTH=30 HEIGHT=0>Mrs. Anigbo, 54, was indicted on one count of simple assault on Miss Ferrechio, two counts of simple assault on D.C. police Officers David C. Poe Jr. and Darrell Best, and one charge of taking property without right. That charge refers to Miss Ferrechio's yellow legal pad, which she carried with her on the visit to the school and which has not been returned.<BR><IMG SRC="../images/nop.gif" ALT="" ALIGN=top WIDTH=30 HEIGHT=0>Neither Mrs. Anigbo nor Miss Ferrechio had comment last night, nor did editors at The Times.<BR><IMG SRC="../images/nop.gif" ALT="" ALIGN=top WIDTH=30 HEIGHT=0>"The grand jury was convened under the guise of investigating felonies. They have returned a misdemeanor indictment," said Veronice Holt, Mrs. Anigbo's attorney.<BR><IMG SRC="../images/nop.gif" ALT="" ALIGN=top WIDTH=30 HEIGHT=0>Still, Miss Holt said, she had no faith in prosecutors who "have demonstrated that they are proceeding in a way that is unjust and does not and will not command the respect of the Washington majority community."<BR><IMG SRC="../images/nop.gif" ALT="" ALIGN=top WIDTH=30 HEIGHT=0>But U.S. Attorney Eric Holder said the indictments represent the decision of a cross-section of the community.<BR><IMG SRC="../images/nop.gif" ALT="" ALIGN=top WIDTH=30 HEIGHT=0>"People who would seek to use this matter for their own negative purposes must be ignored, and people of good faith must step forward and ensure that this matter does not become a divisive issue in our city in the weeks and months ahead," Mr. Holder said in a prepared statement.<BR><IMG SRC="../images/nop.gif" ALT="" ALIGN=top WIDTH=30 HEIGHT=0>Henry S. Hoberman, an attorney for The Times, said: "We are pleased that the grand jury, a true cross-section of our community, spoke with one loud and clear voice against this kind of vitriol and violence."<BR><IMG SRC="../images/nop.gif" ALT="" ALIGN=top WIDTH=30 HEIGHT=0>Besides Mrs. Anigbo, the grand jury indicted Garvey office manager Brenda Gatlin, 36, on counts of simple assault against Miss Ferrechio and photographer Cliff Owen and a count of taking property without right in connection with the missing note pad.<BR><IMG SRC="../images/nop.gif" ALT="" ALIGN=top WIDTH=30 HEIGHT=0>Garvey kindergarten teacher Serena Smith, 41, was indicted on one count each of simple assault on Miss Ferrechio, Officer Poe and Officer Best and one count of taking property without right, for briefly taking Mr. Owen's camera.<BR><IMG SRC="../images/nop.gif" ALT="" ALIGN=top WIDTH=30 HEIGHT=0>The indictments also named a man, known to the grand jury only by the last name of Smith, on a count of simple assault against Officer Poe. Prosecutors are trying to determine who the man is.<BR><IMG SRC="../images/nop.gif" ALT="" ALIGN=top WIDTH=30 HEIGHT=0>All of the charges are misdemeanors, and each carries a maximum sentence of up to 180 days in jail. <BR><IMG SRC="../images/nop.gif" ALT="" ALIGN=top WIDTH=160 HEIGHT=0>By Karyn Spellman<BR><IMG SRC="../images/nop.gif" ALT="" ALIGN=top WIDTH=160 HEIGHT=0>and Kristan Trugman</TD></TR></TABLE> <TD ALIGN=Left VALIGN=Top COLSPAN=1 ROWSPAN=1><TABLE BORDER=0 CELLSPACING=0 CELLPADDING=0 WIDTH=12><TR ALIGN=Left VALIGN=Top> <TD ALIGN=left VALIGN=Top COLSPAN="1" ROWSPAN="1"><IMG SRC="../images/vertical.gif" WIDTH=9 HEIGHT=60 ALIGN=MIDDLE ALT="" border=0></TD></TR></TABLE> <TD ALIGN=Left VALIGN=Top COLSPAN=1 ROWSPAN=1><TABLE BORDER=0 CELLSPACING=0 CELLPADDING=0 WIDTH=180><TR ALIGN=Left VALIGN=Top><TD ALIGN=Left VALIGN=Top COLSPAN=1 ROWSPAN=1><A HREF="about.map"><MAP NAME="clientmap10"><AREA SHAPE=RECT COORDS="1,3,180,59" HREF="aboutnwe.html"></MAP><IMG SRC="images/about.gif" WIDTH=180 HEIGHT=60 ALIGN=MIDDLE border=0 USEMAP="#clientmap10" ISMAP></A></TD></TD></TABLE></TD></TD></TABLE><center><p><a href="#linkTOP">Go back to the top of this page.</A></center></TD></TR>
